						<div class="postbody">EDIT: here's two screenshots - the beginning and the vertical scroll parts.
<br />
<br /><img src="http://rocknes.kinox.org/cv3_1.jpg" alt="Image" /> <img src="http://rocknes.kinox.org/cv3_2.jpg" alt="Image" />
